{"tid":1971321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部重申中國沒有歧視來自「非洲的兄弟」，美方試圖挑動中非之間的衝突不會成功","createTime":"2020-04-13T22:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T07:28:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb22c601aed5c12c79d9299a4d4878e5839b9ac","tid":1971321,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T22:24:14.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部重申，中國沒有歧視來自「非洲的兄弟」，對於美國傳媒報道指非洲人在廣州受到歧視，重申美方試圖挑動中非之間的衝突不會成功。<br />\n<br />\n內地實施嚴格防疫措施，避免更多新型肺炎輸入個案，據報有在廣州的非洲人遭到歧視，包括被業主趕走，要淪落街頭，多個非洲國家去信中國外長王毅，表達強烈關切，認為這些污名化與歧視行為，令人誤以為病毒是非洲人散播。<br />\n<br />\n廣州市政府亦表示，堅持無差別對待原則，公安局說，在實施防疫措施的過程中，對所有中國公民及外籍人士一視同仁，所有外籍人士必須嚴格遵守中國法律，配合防疫工作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520368-20200413.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520368-20200413.htm&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B8wRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=9c15aaa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520368-20200413.htm&h=232c61a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520368-20200413.htm</a>"},{"pid":"31e7085a52c44af3cc349a49b21b93cb23a18fe1","tid":1971321,"uid":50457,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T22:25:44.000Z","msg":"關美國咩事？明明非洲國家抗議"},{"pid":"97792f13f87c9174317872f4ff73afe3d24b1515","tid":1971321,"uid":62,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T22:30:20.000Z","msg":"有哂片都可以屈美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c79f91281a735b911419e88ead907c4ceb5755","tid":1971321,"uid":49776,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T22:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ABVZDr1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FABVZDr1.png&h=afc9b0d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"401245a5ef06db6be462c4560ddd4c01d88efbb6","tid":1971321,"u